    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Playtime</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>It's like a dying wish </l>
          <l>Every day is a race </l>
          <l>A race to the unknown </l>
          <l>Something inside is burning </l>
          <l>Burning the illusions </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>You're feeling inside me </l>
          <l>You're running to hide from pain </l>
          <l>Na,na,na,na,na,na,na </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>You've wasted those few years </l>
          <l>Hiding between fears, the end </l>
          <l>Na,na,na,na,na,na,na </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>You're losing your mind </l>
          <l>Trying to find the way </l>
          <l>Na,na,na,na,na,na,na </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>Going threw pictures </l>
          <l>Photos-it's all the same </l>
          <l>Na,na,na,na,na,na,na </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>Pressure, pressure in my head </l>
          <l>I cannot understand it... </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="7" type="stanza">
          <l>You ask for my help </l>
          <l>Your feeling you can't hold on </l>
          <l>Na,na,na,na,na,na,na </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="8" type="stanza">
          <l>I give you my power </l>
          <l>And burning desire of truth </l>
          <l>Na,na,na,na,na,na,na</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
